      "source": [
        "# Student Attendance Analysis in Google Colab\n",
        "\n",
        "# Step 1: Import Libraries\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "import seaborn as sns\n",
        "\n",
        "# Step 2: Create a Sample Dataset\n",
        "# (You can replace this with your own CSV upload)\n",
        "np.random.seed(42)\n",
        "\n",
        "students = [\"Aman\", \"Priya\", \"Rohit\", \"Sneha\", \"Arjun\", \"Meera\", \"Karan\", \"Anjali\", \"Ravi\", \"Pooja\"]\n",
        "departments = [\"CSE\", \"ECE\", \"ME\", \"CIVIL\"]\n",
        "subjects = [\"Maths\", \"Physics\", \"Computer\", \"English\"]\n",
        "\n",
        "data = []\n",
        "for day in pd.date_range(start=\"2025-01-01\", end=\"2025-01-20\"):\n",
        "    for s in students:\n",
        "        record = {\n",
        "            \"Date\": day,\n",
        "            \"Student\": s,\n",
        "            \"Department\": np.random.choice(departments),\n",
        "            \"Subject\": np.random.choice(subjects),\n",
        "            \"Status\": np.random.choice([\"Present\", \"Absent\"], p=[0.8, 0.2])\n",
        "        }\n",
        "        data.append(record)\n",
        "\n",
        "df = pd.DataFrame(data)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Step 3: Basic Dataset Info\n",
        "print(\"First 10 rows of dataset:\")\n",
        "print(df.head(10))\n",
        "print(\"\\nTotal Records:\", len(df))\n",
        "\n",
        "# Step 4: Attendance Percentage per Student\n",
        "attendance_summary = df.groupby(\"Student\")[\"Status\"].apply(\n",
        "    lambda x: (x == \"Present\").mean() * 100\n",
        ").reset_index(name=\"Attendance %\")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"\\nStudent-wise Attendance Percentage:\")\n",
        "print(attendance_summary)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Step 5: Department-wise Attendance %\n",
        "dept_summary = df.groupby(\"Department\")[\"Status\"].apply(\n",
        "    lambda x: (x == \"Present\").mean() * 100\n",
        ").reset_index(name=\"Dept Attendance %\")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"\\nDepartment-wise Attendance Percentage:\")\n",
        "print(dept_summary)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Step 6: Subject-wise Attendance %\n",
        "subject_summary = df.groupby(\"Subject\")[\"Status\"].apply(\n",
        "    lambda x: (x == \"Present\").mean() * 100\n",
        ").reset_index(name=\"Subject Attendance %\")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"\\nSubject-wise Attendance Percentage:\")\n",
        "print(subject_summary)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Step 7: Visualization - Student Attendance\n",
        "plt.figure(figsize=(10,6))\n",
        "sns.barplot(x=\"Student\", y=\"Attendance %\", data=attendance_summary, palette=\"viridis\")\n",
        "plt.xticks(rotation=45)\n",
        "plt.title(\"Student Attendance Percentage\")\n",
        "plt.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Step 8: Visualization - Department Attendance\n",
        "plt.figure(figsize=(6,4))\n",
        "sns.barplot(x=\"Department\", y=\"Dept Attendance %\", data=dept_summary, palette=\"magma\")\n",
        "plt.title(\"Department-wise Attendance Percentage\")\n",
        "plt.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Step 9: Visualization - Subject Attendance\n",
        "plt.figure(figsize=(6,4))\n",
        "sns.barplot(x=\"Subject\", y=\"Subject Attendance %\", data=subject_summary, palette=\"coolwarm\")\n",
        "plt.title(\"Subject-wise Attendance Percentage\")\n",
        "plt.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Step 10: Attendance Heatmap (Date vs Student)\n",
        "pivot = df.pivot_table(index=\"Date\", columns=\"Student\", values=\"Status\", aggfunc=lambda x: (x==\"Present\").mean())\n",
        "plt.figure(figsize=(12,6))\n",
        "sns.heatmap(pivot, cmap=\"Greens\", cbar_kws={'label': 'Attendance Rate'})\n",
        "plt.title(\"Daily Attendance Heatmap (1=Present, 0=Absent)\")\n",
        "plt.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Step 11: Overall Attendance Pie Chart\n",
        "labels = [\"Present\", \"Absent\"]\n",
        "sizes = df[\"Status\"].value_counts().values\n",
        "colors = [\"#4CAF50\", \"#F44336\"]\n",
        "plt.pie(sizes, labels=labels, autopct='%1.1f%%', colors=colors, startangle=90)\n",
        "plt.title(\"Overall Attendance Distribution\")\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ]
    }
  ]
